reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Stylish and Versatile Creative Companion! - 5 Stars
reviews.reviewText: The Omezizy T02 Pocket Printer Set is a fantastic blend of functionality and aesthetic appeal. This compact printer, bundled with 3 Rolls of 50mm Thermal Paper (2 Rolls Sticky & 1 Roll Non-Sticky), makes for an ideal gift for various occasions like birthdays, Christmas, Thanksgiving, or back-to-school events. The T02 Printer goes beyond mere printing; it becomes a reliable study companion for kids, offering a portable study helper at their fingertips.This Print Pod is not just a printer; it's the ultimate toy for all creative endeavors. Whether you're into scrapbooking, bullet journaling, making checklists, organizing with labels, or capturing cherished moments with pictures, this mini printer sticker maker is ready for your creative exploration. Using the T02 Printer is a breeze with Bluetooth wireless connectivity through the "Phomemo" application, compatible with IOS 9.0 & Android 4.0 and above. The mini thermal printer boasts a 1000mAh rechargeable battery, providing a week's worth of usage on a full charge, with the added convenience of fast charging through the included USB-C cable.Stay inspired with weekly updated templates available on the official application, offering various features like calendars, forms, lists, festival graphics, and early education modules. The T02 Printer allows for adjustable print density, seamlessly working with various 50/53mm thermal papers, including plain paper and sticker paper in white, color, and transparent options.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I couldn’t load the sticker roll at first but I was doing it wrong! Great value for money. I created labels for storage in the loft and it was really easy.I wrote them on word on my iPhone and screen shot the images, saved as photos then printed using the app. Really easy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Amgreat little thermal printer.This little printer is easy to connect to your mobile device (phone, tablet etc.) all you need do is download the free app, connect via Bluetooth and that's it ready to print.There are some sticky labels provided with the printer so you are able to try it out without the need to purchase any additional items. The printer only prints in black but there are coloured sticky labels available if you want to brighten up your labels. This printer can print images as well as text - even photo's from your photo album and the great thing is that, unlike thermal printing in the past, these prints are said to last for up to 10 years!With a rechargeable battery and being of such a diminutive size (roughly the size of a matchbox) this is a truly portable device which you could find many different uses for. Highly recommended especially at the current price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a nifty little printer that has really come in handy recently.It's a compact little thing (roughly 8.5cm square) and is simple and easy to use. It charged via USB C and requires you to download an app in order to use it. I am using it with an iPhone 13 Pro Max and it's works perfectly.It comes with one roll of thermal sticky paper which you need to align before first use. You then can design your sticker in the app and it will print. The quality is what I would expect of a sticker printer - not photo quality just simple and basic.I've been using it to print stickers for my meals I've been prepping for work and they adhere well to the plastic tubs.Its currently priced around £37 which I think is a bit too expensive - At this price I'd expect to kit to be a bit more comprehensive with at least the inclusion of some more thermal sticker paper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: Quick and easy to use label printer
reviews.reviewText: Great little thermal label printer with an easy app to use with many features and designs.With the thermal paper setup as per the guide and app downloaded and paired, the printer is ready to print any thing you want.The app is intuitive and simple to use and prints are clear and crisp.Charging is easy via the provided usb cable and hence the printer is easy to take around with you and just needs to be connected to your phone.
